### Get All Books
GET http://localhost:8000/api/books/
Accept: application/json

### Create a Book
POST http://localhost:8000/api/books/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Pragmatic Programmer",
  "author": "Andrew Hunt",
  "genre": "Programming",
  "published_year": 1999
}

### Get Book Details
GET http://localhost:8000/api/books/1/
Accept: application/json

### Create a Review
POST http://localhost:8000/api/reviews/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "book": 1,
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Excellent book for software engineers!",
  "timestamp": "2025-04-21T10:00:00Z"
}

### Get All Reviews
GET http://localhost:8000/api/reviews/
Accept: application/json

### Update a Review
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/reviews/1/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "book": 1,
  "rating": 4,
  "comment": "Still great, but a bit dated.",
  "timestamp": "2025-04-21T10:10:00Z"
}

### Delete a Review
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/reviews/1/